<br />

<br />
If I answer the question incorrectly, the user gets rejected and my admin email gets the textual confirmation email.
<br />

<br />
But since the web page never advances to the next screen after the &quot;submit&quot; button is hit, the new user is left to wonder if his registration attempt has been approved.
<br />

